.TH NYXUS 1 "May 2026" "NYXUS 2026.05" "NYXUS Manual"
.SH NAME
nyxus \- launcher and dispatcher for NYXUS apps
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nyxus
[\fIMODULE\fR] [\fIARGS...\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Launches the named NYXUS module from /opt/nyxus/nyxus_<MODULE>.py with
the python interpreter. Run without arguments to list available modules.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B NYXUS_HOME
Override the install prefix (defaults to /opt/nyxus).
.SH FILES
/opt/nyxus/, ~/.cache/nyxus/<module>.log
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR nyxus-doctor (1),
.BR nyxus-bootstrap (1)
